    "title": "Actions during the hurricane or storm",
    "description": "Actions to be taken while hurricane or storm conditions are in effect.",
    "content": "# Actions during the hurricane or storm\r\n\r\nThese actions apply during active hurricane or storm conditions. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- All staff, except those required on duty in Meteorological, Security, and Electrical departments and one maintenance technician, should weather the storm at home.\r\n- Manager of Meteorology or designated Officer in Charge must maintain contact with:\r\n  - General Manager\r\n  - Manager of Air Traffic Services\r\n  - Director of Operations\r\n  - National Disaster Management Agency / National Emergency Advisory Council\r\n- All security officers should remain within the designated terminal building area.\r\n- Employees required to work during tropical cyclone conditions will be assisted by the Authority with essential domestic affairs as necessary.",
