    "title": "Objectives",
    "description": "Objectives of the GAA Tropical Cyclone Emergency Plan.",
    "content": "# Objectives\r\n\r\nThis section states the intended outcomes of the Tropical Cyclone Emergency Plan and aligns departments around shared priorities. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Plan objectives\r\n\r\n- Create a comprehensive, simplified, and direct plan of action for GAA in the event of a tropical cyclone threat or impact.\r\n- Ensure each department fully understands its role and responsibilities to reduce duplication and streamline preparedness activities.\r\n- Ensure effective communication between departments for successful emergency management.\r\n- Ensure that the team identified to operate the Emergency Operations Centre (EOC) at MBIA is activated in the shortest possible time.\r\n\r\n## Expected result\r\n\r\nWhen executed as designed, these objectives support safer operations, faster coordination, and quicker restoration of airport services.",
