    "content": "# Pre-season actions: Air Traffic\r\n\r\nThe Manager of Air Traffic Services or designate should complete critical communications and equipment checks before season start. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- Coordinate with ECCAA technicians to ensure waterproof cover is available for ATC console and electronic equipment in the Technical Block, VOR, and NDB buildings.\r\n- Liaise with ECCAA technicians to confirm all portable air/ground radios are operational.",
