    "title": "Pre-season actions: Met Department",
    "description": "Pre-season preparedness actions for the Meteorological Department.",
    "content": "# Pre-season actions: Met Department\r\n\r\nThe Manager of Meteorology or designate ensures staffing, supplies, and communication readiness before season start. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Consumables and equipment\r\n\r\n- Ensure adequate stock of paper (8.5x11 and 8.5x14).\r\n- Ensure printer, photocopier, and fax cartridges are available.\r\n- Ensure flashlights, batteries, and first-aid supplies are available.\r\n\r\n## Coordination and contact readiness\r\n\r\n- Inform the Meteorological Office at Piarco (Trinidad) of work and home contact numbers for:\r\n  - Manager of Meteorology\r\n  - Assistant Manager of Meteorology\r\n- Prepare and maintain phone/fax list for disaster preparedness officials and National Disaster Management Agency / National Emergency Advisory Council contacts.\r\n\r\n## Staff preparation\r\n\r\n- Conduct staff discussions on procedures during the hurricane season.",
