    "description": "Pre-season preparedness actions for Security and Emergency Services.",
    "content": "# Pre-season actions: Security\r\n\r\nThe Security Manager or designate prepares lighting, communications, and emergency support supplies before season start. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- Ensure all spotlights and flashlights are serviceable.\r\n- Ensure all security radios are serviceable.\r\n- Prepare and maintain an emergency foodstuff list.",
