    "title": "Representation",
    "description": "EOC representation and leadership roles under the Hurricane Plan.",
    "content": "# Representation\r\n\r\nThe following positions are represented in the team responsible for managing the Emergency Operations Centre (EOC) during an emergency. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## EOC representation\r\n\r\n- General Manager\r\n- Director of Operations\r\n- Manager of Meteorology\r\n- Manager of Security\r\n- Manager of Air Traffic Services\r\n- Manager of Maintenance\r\n- Manager of Human Resources\r\n- Officer in Charge of CFR\r\n- Duty Managers\r\n- Quality Assurance and Compliance Manager\r\n- Airline representative\r\n- Refueling agent representative\r\n- Officer in Charge (Lauriston)\r\n\r\n## EOC coordination\r\n\r\nThe General Manager assumes the role of EOC Coordinator when it is imminent that a tropical cyclone will strike Grenada.",
