    "title": "Warning issued actions: Administration",
    "description": "Administration actions when a storm or hurricane warning is issued.",
    "content": "# Warning issued actions: Administration\r\n\r\nAdministration teams should protect IT and communications functions needed for continuity during storm impact. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Information Technology Centre\r\n\r\n- Run a full backup and secure backup drive in the safe.\r\n- Disconnect and secure power supply units, computers, and printers.\r\n- Ensure Meteorological Services telecommunications systems and internet links are operational.\r\n\r\n## PABX operators\r\n\r\n- Ensure all telephone lines are clear and available.\r\n- Direct all tropical cyclone calls and enquiries to the National Disaster Management Agency.",
