    "title": "Warning issued actions: Carriacou",
    "description": "Carriacou airport actions when warning is issued.",
    "content": "# Warning issued actions: Carriacou\r\n\r\nThe Manager of Air Traffic Services should liaise with the Officer in Charge of Carriacou to complete the following actions. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- Secure the air/ground radio.\r\n- Take down and secure windsock.\r\n- Secure the terminal building.\r\n- Take down and secure VHF antenna.",
