    "title": "Warning issued actions: CFR",
    "description": "Crash Fire Rescue actions when warning is issued.",
    "content": "# Warning issued actions: CFR\r\n\r\nCrash Fire Rescue should secure response assets and maintain emergency support readiness. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- Secure all rescue vehicles in designated areas.\r\n- Check all radios and flashlights.\r\n- Liaise with Building Maintenance Foreman to secure Fire Hall areas requiring reinforcement.\r\n- Ensure first-aid kits are properly stocked.",
