    "title": "Warning issued actions: ECCAA",
    "description": "ECCAA technical actions when a storm or hurricane warning is issued.",
    "content": "# Warning issued actions: ECCAA\r\n\r\nECCAA technical specialists should execute the following equipment-protection steps during warning phase. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- Secure all portable radios.\r\n- Cover all electronic equipment including VOR/DME, NDB, receivers, and transmitters.\r\n- Take down all VHF antennas and secure them.",
