    "title": "Warning issued actions: Security",
    "description": "Security and Emergency Services actions when warning is issued.",
    "content": "# Warning issued actions: Security\r\n\r\nSecurity and Emergency Services should transition to standby posture and sustain on-duty operations through event passage. {{ className: 'lead' }}\r\n\r\n## Action checklist\r\n\r\n- Inform all off-duty security officers to remain on standby.\r\n- Ensure flashlights and gas lanterns are equipped and in working order.\r\n- Check security vehicle fuel, oil, and operating condition.\r\n- Check all security radios.\r\n- Instruct all security officers on duty to remain on duty until relieved.\r\n- Make available emergency foodstuff items for duty staff.",
